org.hibernate.query.sqm.mutation.spi.idtable

Class PersistentTableStrategy

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hibernate.query.sqm.mutation.spi.idtable.AbstractTableBasedMutationStrategy
      • org.hibernate.query.sqm.mutation.spi.idtable.PersistentTableStrategy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SqmMutationStrategy

    public class PersistentTableStrategy
extends AbstractTableBasedMutationStrategy
    This is a strategy that mimics temporary tables for databases which do not support temporary tables. It follows a pattern similar to the ANSI SQL definition of global temporary table using a "session id" column to segment rows from the various sessions.
